  <brief_title>High Risk Primitive Neuroectodermal (PNET) Brain Tumors in Childhood</brief_title>
  <official_title>Treatment Protocol for High-Risk PNET Brain Tumors in Children With Surgery, Sequential Chemotherapy, Conventional and High-Dose With Peripheral Blood Stem Cell Transplantation and Radiation Therapy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Gustave Roussy, Cancer Campus, Grand Paris</agency>
