    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Gustave Roussy, Cancer Campus, Grand Paris</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy of the combination of surgery,
      conventional chemotherapy, sequential high-dose chemotherapy with peripheral blood stem cell
      transplantation and reduced dose radiation therapy in high-risk PNET brain tumors.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
